About the game: Play as an anthropomorphic computer virus in prog.1. When world-renowned scientists Dr. Cushing and Dr. Keiko are assigned to the secret G.A.i.A project, their attempt to construct a digital universe takes a turn for the worse when they accidentally unleash a sentient computer virus. Can you get through 48 levels filled to the brim with challenging platforming and puzzle solving to finally uncover the truth about the digital world?
